<b>Esercizio 5A</b> Scrivere un programma che legge un reale e stampa
unmessaggio secondo la seguente tabella:
<p></p>
<center>
<table border="2" cellpadding="3">
  <tbody>
    <tr align="center">
      <th>gradi alcolici g</th>
      <th>messaggio</th>
    </tr>
    <tr align="center">
      <td>40 &lt; g</td>
      <td>superalcolico</td>
    </tr>
    <tr align="center">
      <td>20 &lt; g &lt;= 40</td>
      <td>alcolico</td>
    </tr>
    <tr align="center">
      <td>15 &lt; g &lt;= 20</td>
      <td>liquore</td>
    </tr>
    <tr align="center">
      <td>12 &lt; g &lt;= 15</td>
      <td>vino forte</td>
    </tr>
    <tr align="center">
      <td>10.5 &lt; g &lt;= 12</td>
      <td>vino normale</td>
    </tr>
    <tr align="center">
      <td>g &lt;= 10.5</td>
      <td>vino leggero</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
